係唔係就咁用FTP SOFTWARE直接DOM上WEB HOSTING就得? <br />\n因為我的認知仲係十幾年前寫完個HTML網就咁UPLOAD上WEB黎開<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n簡單法：<br />\n1.選個hosting,  用git push d code上github<br />\n2.ssh入去server,  pull d code落黎<br />\n3.node個js檔 或者 用forever等等run server既module,  run你個網站<br />\n4. 完成"},{"pid":"077e9602fbaca9dcd5dee7a660d4d459377b2ae5","tid":348429,"uid":23094,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-06T13:33:25.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>我想問用NODEJS寫完的網係唔係就咁用FTP SOFTWARE直接DOM上WEB HOSTING就得? <br />\n因為我的認知仲係十幾年前寫完個HTML網就咁UPLOAD上WEB黎開<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n簡單法：<br />\n1.選個hosting,  用git push d code上github<br />\n2.ssh入去server,  pull d code落黎<br />\n3.node個js檔 或者 用forever等等run server既module,  run你個網站<br />\n4. 完成</blockquote><br />\npm2好用啲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"12ffdf186df378931cfcf146f6e2564c00c39a70","tid":348429,"uid":61249,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-07T04:22:34.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>我想問用NODEJS寫完的網係唔係就咁用FTP SOFTWARE直接DOM上WEB HOSTING就得? <br />\n因為我的認知仲係十幾年前寫完個HTML網就咁UPLOAD上WEB黎開<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n個concept同以前一樣，例如apache, php 既backend組合, nodejs就用express 框架做<br />\n如果你淨係做frontend (唔連backend 拎data), 你咪同以前一樣直接upload html, js 上web hosting, 因為個web host 個folder本來就係apache server. nodejs 只係你開發果部機用, 用黎將你d react, angular, vue 等file 變做es5的js"},{"pid":"85576f3c0e4fb7c03642a4f230c7575867d3a878","tid":348429,"uid":85524,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-07T04:31:36.000Z","msg":"有冇人可以 深入淺出nginx ? <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"77ad936d5a4f66823efdd542f2795adaf8195a42","tid":348429,"uid":35077,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-08T05:33:03.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>我想問用NODEJS寫完的網係唔係就咁用FTP SOFTWARE直接DOM上WEB HOSTING就得? <br />\n因為我的認知仲係十幾年前寫完個HTML網就咁UPLOAD上WEB黎開<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n個concept同以前一樣，例如apache, php 既backend組合, nodejs就用express 框架做<br />\n如果你淨係做frontend (唔連backend 拎data), 你咪同以前一樣直接upload html, js 上web hosting, 因為個web host 個folder本來就係apache server. nodejs 只係你開發果部機用, 用黎將你d react, angular, vue 等file 變做es5的js</blockquote><br />\n除非有 JS server side logic<br />\n否則用 babel / webpack 打埋一舊掟上去就係<br />\n<br />\n專有名詞轉哂，但實質流程都係咁上下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"28b14954f6b39e8f5c4a3c8cf45967035c7c5663","tid":348429,"uid":65030,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-20T14:55:48.000Z","msg":"岩岩申請左個cloudflare 但完全唔知點upload 我個web 上去<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3ff51ef1d4d3826fc1e768f1d2ab9f0c8f297cca","tid":348429,"uid":1573,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-20T17:15:59.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.heroku.com/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.heroku.com%2F&d=J637X6iL2XvI4RNe%2FZAEg5zN29kXmk9bB7xBuKM86BA%3D&h=c582d8c6\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.heroku.com/</a><br />\n你可以去開個free app試住先，到時真係要出街再租個$5 usd vps"}]}